        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4128623940" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer3217412516956825080">I enjoyed this murder mystery! Thank you to the author for asking me to read this book. It was full of twists and turns so I had to pay attention but wrapped up real good. Local journalist is found dead at the pool and authorities dismissed it as an overdose. Aurora starts investigating as her friend is convinced it wasn’t a suicide. She ends up discovering a few more murders and in the end the truth is revealed. It was slow to start but warms up and keeps you til the end of the book. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


