  <span id="freeText17374360525680593953" style="display:none">I received a free Ecopy of the book in exchange for an honest review<br />I really liked the characters. Aurora, Suz, Candice, John, and Nicolas. The development and conversations were believable and well done. <br />I think for me I did not enjoy the format of the book. It was confusing at first because the two stories didn't seem to connect and it just wasn't making sense why this additional plot was happening at the end of each chapter. The last 50 pages it all came together and I understood.<br />The book was entertaining but, it was not really my thing. I think others will love it and it was definitely worth reading.</span>
