        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4175838993" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer16482042664912357555">I have to say <b>If Shadows Could Tell</b> by Granthana Sinha has one of the most unusual covers I&apos;ve come across. That&apos;s saying something since my bookshelf is stuffed with mysteries and thrillers. The enlarged image of the blood stained fingerprint was a sure eye catcher.<br/>I had heard so much about this book from a friend and ended up purchasing a copy.<br/>The book was intense, twisty, thrilling and fully captivating. It had all the elements of a good psychological thriller with a great ending. <br/>This was my</span>
  <span id="freeText16482042664912357555" style="display:none">I have to say <b>If Shadows Could Tell</b> by Granthana Sinha has one of the most unusual covers I've come across. That's saying something since my bookshelf is stuffed with mysteries and thrillers. The enlarged image of the blood stained fingerprint was a sure eye catcher.<br />I had heard so much about this book from a friend and ended up purchasing a copy.<br />The book was intense, twisty, thrilling and fully captivating. It had all the elements of a good psychological thriller with a great ending. <br />This was my first book by this author and she did a great job with the twists. <br />I would recommend it as a must-read thriller!</span>
