  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/4228140343" />
    <a title="Dave Wheeler" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/17131731-dave-wheeler"><img alt="Dave Wheeler" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1359997984p2/17131731.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/4228140343?book_show_action=true">Sep 17, 2021</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Dave Wheeler" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Dave Wheeler" href="/user/show/17131731-dave-wheeler">Dave Wheeler</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was amazing"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was amazing</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span></span>

          <span class="greyText">&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;</span>
          <a class="lightGreyText" title="Kindle Edition " href="/book/show/55713733-if-shadows-could-tell">review of another edition</a>


        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4228140343" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer1925986210013936432">This is a Thriller to love <br/><br/>So this is a story that&apos;s starts at at funeral, well after the prologue that is, and Aurora had to find the truth. There are several people who want the truth including Candice, Nicolas and John plus Suz&apos;s Auras bff.<br/><br/>When Janet a young journalist goes missing Suz is worried and tries to get Aurora to help find her but it&apos;s not good news and Aura sets out or rather is encouraged to find the truth. On top of this during a bad day Aurora accidentally gatecrashes a funeral </span>
  <span id="freeText1925986210013936432" style="display:none">This is a Thriller to love <br /><br />So this is a story that's starts at at funeral, well after the prologue that is, and Aurora had to find the truth. There are several people who want the truth including Candice, Nicolas and John plus Suz's Auras bff.<br /><br />When Janet a young journalist goes missing Suz is worried and tries to get Aurora to help find her but it's not good news and Aura sets out or rather is encouraged to find the truth. On top of this during a bad day Aurora accidentally gatecrashes a funeral (don't we all) and meets the strange Nicolas Davenport who appears in several places that Aura just happens to be in.<br /><br />There are several interesting characters you meet and each had a part in this Thriller that will grab you surprise you and at times dumfound you in the right ways. The ending week it's not what you expect but isn't that what you want it to be I hate predictable personally.<br /><br />So why 5 stars well when you read it you will see, for me it would be wrong for any less it had my attention I didn't want to put it down and well who needs food, well not till I finished anyway.</span>
  <a data-text-id="1925986210013936432" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

